## CH5  •  Darkrock is #1

[[31 July 2024]]

EXT. Square in London

[[TBA]]

DARKROCK
2038!  The most prosperous time, the best year of your lives!  Hello, citizen of Earth!

Crowd applauses.

DARKROCK (CONT’D)
Yes, I know, I know, you *love* this title!  And thank goodness, I helped you to *learn* to love it!  Today I’m in London.  But no matter where I am, I’m always in your hearts!  Translated to every language for every nation in the world!

Crowd applauses.

DARKROCK (CONT’D)
Yes, thank you, thank you!  Well, progress update, everyone!  On the other hand, I don’t speak other language, right?

Crowd laughs.

DARKROCK (CONT’D)
I’m still on my way to make this planet as technologically advanced as you can imagine, and even beyond it!  Today I want to talk about the most influencing people.  You!

Crowd laughs.

DARKROCK (CONT’D)
Okay, I know, I know.  You did expect this joke.  Although it’s still true.  There’s no need to talk about you, fantastic people.  You know very well who I was going to talk about.  Well, it takes some time to talk some sense to Elon Musk.

Crowd laughs hysterically.

DARKROCK (CONT’D)
Ah yeah, that guy puts crosses on just about anything.  Return damn blue bird, man.  But two days ago, I was talking to Pavel Durov.  Absolutely wonderful person.  It still surprises me extremely that since 2036 he’s on very cordial terms with WhatsApp.  Couldn’t be imagined a couple of decades ago, am I right?  Their approaches to work are still significantly different, but as you know, they are very cooperative.  When could you imagine being able to run your own private WhatsApp server that is open-source?

Crowd applauses.

DARKROCK (CONT’D)
So.  We’ve agreed with various companies to form an alliance, and we’ve agreed to start working on a universal fully cloud-based operating system.  Without any of the fake rough stuff you’ve ever seen.  Chrome OS, seriously?  Never again!

Crowd applauses and laughs.

DARKROCK (CONT’D)
I am currently in talks with large corporations to make their server capacity available.  Moreover, I am pushing the process of financing infrastructure.  Web3-compatible.  It’s going to be a digital paradise for everyone!  Cross-platform like never before!  And I suggest we stop any talk about privacy and security - we’ve already closed those topics for you!

Crowd is confused.

DARKROCK (CONT’D)
I know, you’re not ready to make this step.  We must stop this perpetual addiction to privacy that has become a global paranoia.  Seriously, since the mass hysteria began, several standards for calculating privacy levels have been invented, through a joint effort with EFF.  So, when in your life has that mark fallen below the recommended level?

A pensive murmur hung among the people.

DARKROCK (CONT’D)
I’ll say even more, the vast majority have the maximum level.  Therefore, we will be taking steps to abandon any privacy metrics in the near future.  Your digital worlds have already reached the limit of privacy!  It is default!  Everywhere!

